### QUICK TEST - P2P Energy Trading Backend
### Run these tests in order

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000

# ============================================
# QUICK START TESTS (Run in Order)
# ============================================

### 1. Is Server Running?
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### 2. Get API Info
GET {{baseUrl}}/

###

### 3. Register Test User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/energy/register-user
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userAddress":"0xe807306ac51250b2bfba6aa173510ea68e525b41",
  "houseId": "TEST_HOUSE_010"
}

###

### 4. Submit Energy Data (Surplus)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/energy/data
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userAddress": "0x772c02a37699d7adad82d16c3478a038a59157b3",
  "consumption": 45000,
  "production": 60000
}

###

### 5. Check User Profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/energy/user/0x772c02a37699d7adad82d16c3478a038a59157b3

###

### 6. Get Current Price
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/price/current

###

### 7. Update Price (Market Simulation)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/price/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "totalSupply": 150000,
  "totalDemand": 120000
}

###

### 8. Check Marketplace
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/marketplace/stats

# ============================================
# SUCCESS INDICATORS:
# ============================================
# ✅ All requests return 200 OK
# ✅ User gets registered
# ✅ Energy data is submitted
# ✅ Tokens are minted for surplus
# ✅ Price updates successfully
# ============================================